videos.headline: Patterson finds Sean McKeon for 17-yard TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson throws a pass to Sean McKeon that McKeon carries 17 yards to open up the scoring for Michigan.

videos.headline: Higdon hustles for 43 yards
videos.description: Karan Higdon runs 43 yards for a Michigan first down early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Higdon takes it to the house
videos.description: Karan Higdon runs 67 yards for a Michigan touchdown on the first play of the drive.

videos.headline: Noah Furbush with the Michigan INT
videos.description: Noah Furbush intercepts Jon Wassink at the 46 yard line for Michigan.

videos.headline: Evans runs for Michigan TD
videos.description: Chris Evans runs 27 yards for a Michigan touchdown as the Wolverines lead 21-0.

videos.headline: Michigan blocks a punt
videos.description: Khaleke Hudson blocks a Western Michigan punt and returns it to the Western Michigan 24-yard line.

videos.headline: Patterson finds Peoples-Jones for Michigan TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson throws a perfect pass to Donovan Peoples-Jones for the 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dylan McCaffrey throws 1st Michigan TD
videos.description: Dylan McCaffrey, younger brother of Christian McCaffrey, throws his first touchdown in a Michigan uniform to Jake McCurry.
